Package: diversityGPT
Title: Universal Diversity Metric Transformation for Microbiome Analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Scott", "Handley", , "scott.handley@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Solves the critical decision confusion problem in microbiome diversity 
    analysis by providing intelligent synthesis of multiple diversity metrics. When 
    different metrics give conflicting results, diversityGPT uses consensus algorithms 
    and AI-powered interpretation to provide clear, actionable insights.
